== Section 1: Educational Media & Social Studies Education ==
This book will highlight, evaluate, and recommend different media and methods for leveraging learning through the use of technology. The main focus of the work is on exposing new and novel formats for teaching in a virtual environment. Everyone is invited to contribute, especially tech-savvy educators, students, and members of the wiki community.

{{TODO| Outline still under construction. Please contribute to the outline by introducing new forms of educational media that can be integrated into the social studies classroom.}}

''    A standardized format for the essay on each educational medium is proposed:   
   1.1 Introduction & Background
   1.2 Definitions
   1.3 Ethics
   1.4 Instructional Use
   1.5 Conclusions and Recommendations
   1.6 Examples & Exemplars
   1.7 Resources
   1.8 References''

